{"tid":230272,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會洗刷國殤之柱","createTime":"2017-05-05T08:43:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T08:47:20.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d734591aa8d146c4fe6abf41e03c42937906cb32","tid":230272,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20011264&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20011264%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170505&d=jO1S1Ej7eDj8oQYGBWUFpE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=0c9eb12d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20011264%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170505&h=802203b7\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20011264&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170505</a><br />\n<br />\n支聯會洗刷國殤之柱<br />\n<br />\n港聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n洗刷國殤之柱乃支聯會每年的傳統。 許頌明攝<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】今年是六四事件28周年，支聯會昨日按傳統到香港大學洗刷「國殤之柱」，出席的10多名成員雨中獻花，悼念六四死難者。支聯會主席何俊仁說行動一方面是紀念五四運動，同時表達強烈的意志，繼續以勇氣及良心向專橫暴政說不。<br />\n去年學聯退出支聯會，多間大專院校不參與支聯會舉辦的六四燭光集會，另外舉行悼念活動。何俊仁昨表示今年的集會安排未落實，尚未知會否有學生組織參與，但強調一定會有青年人代表上台。<br />\n何俊仁說：「如果（學生）覺得要有自己嘅活動，都可以遍地開花，我哋採取互相尊重、包容嘅態度。」他認為只要是支持內地、香港早日實現民主，同時悼念為民主犧牲自由及生命的勇士，相信大家都是站在一起的。"},{"pid":"7abd7efbb40de23e53c4146123f9c89bcd07ef70","tid":230272,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:45:03.000Z","msg":"洗刷國殤之柱乃支聯會每年的傳統。 許頌明攝<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170505/large/05la7p04.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170505%2Flarge%2F05la7p04.jpg&h=05e579cd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"223d6efd158902588b799f0c05724994fdc0444c","tid":230272,"uid":57460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:45:04.000Z","msg":"支聯會全名係咩到底？"},{"pid":"24ef73adc21675a09e3f372a18200843be6b9c92","tid":230272,"uid":34517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T08:47:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支聯會全名係咩到底？</blockquote><br />\n支那聯合會"}]}